item.description:
@PaulT wrote:

There’s plenty of cracked and alpha versions floating around, but they are not very far along developmentally so you are much better off paying for it. Also, unless you know what you’re doing, you are basically fast-tracking yourself into a Russian botnet if you download the private server clients.

With that being said, all you have to do is google this and you should be all set:
Rust Client 17.02.2014
